    GSEA Plot

    GSEAPlot.Rd

    GSEA Plot

    Usage

    GSEAPlot(
  x,
  geneSetID,
  title = NULL,
  subtitle = NULL,
  base_size = 12,
  rel_heights = c(1.5, 0.5, 1),
  subplots = 1:3,
  ES_geom = c("line", "dot"),
  color = "#6BB82D",
  n_coregene = 10,
  sample_coregene = FALSE,
  label_gene = NULL,
  label.fg = "black",
  label.bg = "white",
  label.bg.r = 0.1,
  label.size = 4
)
